summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical distribution easements over portions of the south 80 feet of vacated alley in Block 14, South Seattle; the north 15 feet of Lot "A" of King County Lot Line Adjustment 8805018; vacated South Fidalgo Street lying southerly of the southwesterly production of the northwesterly line of Lot 6, Block 5, Georgetown River Front Addition to Seattle; the east 26 feet of Lots 19 and 20, Sea Breeze Tracts; the west 5 feet of the south 15 feet of Lot 5 and the west 5 feet of Lot 6 together with the north 5 feet of the west 15 feet of Lot 6, except the west 5 feet thereof, Block 44, Lake Union Addition.
